&reftitle.description;

 public intImagickDraw::getStrokeLineJoin


&warn.undocumented.func;


 Returns the shape to be used at the corners of paths (or other vector
 shapes) when they are stroked.

&reftitle.returnvalues;


 Returns a LINEJOIN constant
 (imagick::LINEJOIN_*), or 0 if stroke line join is not set.
